    intro hξ hhξ;
    -- By definition of `freqDivisor �`,� if `freqDivisor q 1 hξ = d`, then there exists some `a : Fin 1 → ZMod d` such that `hξ = fun i => (((a i).val * (q / d) : ℕ) : ZMod q)`.
    obtain ⟨a, ha⟩ : ∃ a : Fin 1 → ZMod d, hξ = fun i => (((a i).val * (q / d) : ℕ) : ZMod q) := by
